{"title":"“温情”的双手","authors":["赵曙光"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":8,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“温情”的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“温情”的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像两瓶陈年老酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷醉了他的心头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“温情”的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像甜蜜的安眠药片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖着他呼呼梦里走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“区区小事，不能出卖朋友”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他把这颗黑心紧搂在胸前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派分子不住地点头称赞："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“愿上帝与你同在，好心的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警卫员”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}